channel.title: Looking for a Development team
channel.description:
Hey well I'am wanting to start up a new project and I currently have enough funds for a website, WEBHOST, vps, a few advertisement spots here and there but soon I'll have more funds to put into the server.
Currently looking for the following;
ClientSided Dev ServerSided Dev WebSided Dev Preferrably members with Video editing knowledge to create server videos for youtube (Will be paid depending on the outcome)
If you are interested pm me or add me on skype - i_am_b0b or just reply to this thread.
We will be using this base ; http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/projects/587648-swades.html
